Bernanke Urges Congress to Help Homeowners Refinance

-- B y   C h r i s   W e l l i s z
-- 
2011-10-04T14:51:20Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-04/bernanke-urges-congress-to-help-homeowners-refinance.html
Federal Reserve Chairman Ben S.
Bernanke today urged lawmakers to consider ways to help
homeowners refinance their mortgages as a way to revive the
housing market. He was responding to questions from the Joint
Economic Committee of Congress today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Chris Wellisz at 
 cwellisz@bloomberg.net  